em></a><em>.</em></p><!--/$--><!--$--><div><div><div class=\"bz-campaign bz-campaign-bottom-45896500\" data-nosnippet=\"true\"><div class=\"sc-c014f608-0 kUPEDz skeleton min-h-[inherit] animate-pulse variant\" role=\"status\"><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div></div><div class=\"flex sm:hidden flex-col\"><div class=\"sc-c014f608-0 kUPEDz skeleton min-h-[inherit] animate-pulse variant\" role=\"status\"><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><!--/$--><!--$--><ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.benzinga.com/tech/25/01/43221770/apples-ipad-turns-15-today-heres-a-throwback-to-when-steve-jobs-explained-called-it-the-third-category-after-phones-and-notebooks\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Apple's iPad Turns 15 Today: Here's A Throwback To When Steve Jobs Explained Called It The ‘Third Category' After Phones And Notebooks</a></strong></li>\n</ul><!--/$--><!--$--><!--$--><div class=\"sc-exeBjx kjPTmb raptive-ad-placement mx-auto overflow-hidden min-h-[250px] min-w-[300px] raptive-ad-wrapper flex flex-col items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"raptive-ben-content w-full flex items-center justify-center\" id=\"\"></div></div><!--/$--><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\"><strong><em>Disclaimer: </em></strong><em>This content was partially produced with the help of </em><a href=\"https://www.benzinga.com/author/benzinga-neuro\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Benzinga Neuro</em></a><em> and was reviewed and published by Benzinga editors.</em></p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\"><em>Sundar Pichai | Photo courtesy: Rokas Tenys / 